<plot>The unmarried daughter (Gloria Reubens) of a Texas rancher (Ving Rhames) gives birth to an unwanted child. She puts the child up for adoption and moves away from home. Without her knowledge, her father took the boy and raised him. Twelve years later, she is now a successful family-court judge in L.A. Over the years, she has avoided her father and knows nothing of the child. That all changes when he decides that is time she knew her own child and heads for L.A. However, he quickly finds that she wants nothing to do with her father and cares little about the son she never knew.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?338160</url></doc>
